## Privacy Policy

The Web Page Reader API, built on top of Jina AI's Reader API, does not
collect, store, or share any personal data.

For analytics and performance monitoring, certain non-personal data (such as
request timestamps and headers) is stored in Cloudflare's Analytics Engine for
a duration of three months.
